# ============================================================
# Mapbox GL Token
# ============================================================
# Get your free token at: https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/
#
# 1. Create an account at mapbox.com (free tier gives 50,000
#    map loads/month — more than enough for a hackathon demo)
# 2. Go to Account → Tokens → Create a token (or use the default)
# 3. Copy the "pk.xxxxx..." token
# 4. Rename this file from .env.example to .env
# 5. Paste your token below:
#
# Since this is a Vite project, env vars must be prefixed
# with VITE_ to be accessible in frontend code.
# ============================================================

VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=YOUR_MAPBOX_TOKEN_HERE
